{"tid":2426702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實BTS算唔算改變咗世界？","createTime":"2021-02-28T09:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T09:55:29.000Z","uid":367769,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2b06a3bebfd1a61a05c49a2e88a3026f34289f49","tid":2426702,"uid":367769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:29:37.000Z","msg":"Asian不嬲冇乜地位<br />\n講racism大家一定係諗起BLM先<br />\n但就冇乜人會想幫Asian討回公道<br />\n更何況依家因為武漢肺炎歧視得仲勁<br />\n但係BTS俾個德國人歧視完之後大把唔同國家嘅fans都喺Twitter刷trend<br />\n同BTS合作過Artists都有幫手出聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1jYwaKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1jYwaKh.jpg&h=40ecc315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6uoj34i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uoj34i.jpg&h=76715afd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33OLZCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33OLZCD.jpg&h=42e112ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8VRUSXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8VRUSXD.jpg&h=8b89a131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65wxECE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F65wxECE.png&h=8ba3099a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rDa6J4k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrDa6J4k.png&h=5afa2b71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YxNEjCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYxNEjCF.jpg&h=8c719ebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8MdcECF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8MdcECF.jpg&h=a58c808d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果當初被歧視嗰個唔係BTS而係其他人<br />\n件事會唔會搞到依家咁大？<br />\n上面發聲嘅呢堆人又會唔會出嚟發聲？<br />\n雖然好多連登仔都睇唔起Kpop<br />\n但係無可否認BTS的確成功令到Asian嘅地位提升咗"},{"pid":"ed0c7a1933a847d59a05957fdb9e329bcf5262ab"